(16, 1, '2020-10-13 11:09:40', '2020-10-13 15:09:40', '<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li>Educational Purpose</li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Using online social networks in the educational process has been supported by several educational technology researchers, who have emphasized the benefits of technologies. The rising of social networking sites and a general interest in students have attracted attention to the use of internet tools to develop distance education.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":14,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/educationalPripose.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-14\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2)Worldwide connectivity</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We have the chance to connect with others and share information through social media. It’s the communication that brings us all together, and it’s easily accessible.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":15,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wwconnectivity.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-15\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Reference: <a href=\"https://medium.com/@clinguen/advantages-and-disadvantages-of-social-media-47cd957b73d5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https://medium.com/@clinguen/advantages-and-disadvantages-of-social-media-47cd957b73d5</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Advantages of  Social Media', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-10-13 11:09:40', '2020-10-13 15:09:40', '', 13, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2020/10/13/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(17, 1, '2020-10-13 11:14:56', '2020-10-13 15:14:56', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1. Privacy problems</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sharing your online location or getting in trouble at work because of tweeting something inappropriate or sharing too much with the public can cause you some issues that sometimes can’t ever be solved.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":18,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/privacy.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-18\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2)It changes lifestyle habits, and it is sleep disruption</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;Staring into the light from a computer or phone screen at night can negatively affect your ability to get a proper night sleep.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":19,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/sleep.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-19\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Reference:<a href=\"https://medium.com/@clinguen/advantages-and-disadvantages-of-social-media-47cd957b73d5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"> https://medium.com/@clinguen/advantages-and-disadvantages-of-social-media-47cd957b73d5</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Disadvantages of Social Media', '', 'private', 'open', 'open', '', 'disadvantages-of-social-media', '', '', '2020-10-14 14:42:28', '2020-10-14 18:42:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=17', 0, 'post', '', 0),
