(20, 1, '2020-10-13 11:14:56', '2020-10-13 15:14:56', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1. Privacy problems</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sharing your online location or getting in trouble at work because of tweeting something inappropriate or sharing too much with the public can cause you some issues that sometimes can’t ever be solved.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":18,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/privacy.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-18\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2)It changes lifestyle habits, and it is sleep disruption</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Staring into the light from a computer or phone screen at night can negatively affect your ability to get a proper night sleep.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":19,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/sleep.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-19\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Reference:<a href=\"https://medium.com/@clinguen/advantages-and-disadvantages-of-social-media-47cd957b73d5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"> https://medium.com/@clinguen/advantages-and-disadvantages-of-social-media-47cd957b73d5</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Disadvantages of Social Media', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-10-13 11:14:56', '2020-10-13 15:14:56', '', 17, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2020/10/13/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
